{"tid":2200281,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知「消費者委員會」有咩用？","createTime":"2020-09-12T21:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T07:41:25.000Z","uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5588b492fa25b03ecb3fb81025350467c96ac664","tid":2200281,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:45:33.000Z","msg":"話說，我最近遇到一間黑店。係旺角叫「soundsgoodhk」<br />\n買咗嘢之後，佢成個月都冇比貨，當中，同鋪頭果邊不斷wts，但鋪頭都比唔到一個確實時間幾時有貨。<br />\n最後我要求佢退錢/比貨。但佢2樣都做唔到，不斷用藉口推卻。<br />\n<br />\n而家想睇下報「消費者委員會」定係「海關」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144761fd7b77e102d6c7fec921122b460e512b26","tid":2200281,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fdb2a44c8cdea703426b114152666d84be6848","tid":2200281,"uid":228169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:46:56.000Z","msg":"消委會"},{"pid":"80dab795fb11591cb523ea131d50b191605b9c89","tid":2200281,"uid":142712,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:47:06.000Z","msg":"冇用，報海關有少少用"},{"pid":"ae101e125db6cd248ca10f9db4b7b3ac8d9a9ae2","tid":2200281,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"80dab795fb11591cb523ea131d50b191605b9c89","tid":2200281,"uid":142712,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:47:06.000Z","msg":"冇用，報海關有少少用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:49:01.000Z","msg":"消費者委員會係咪廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁海關會點做？<br />\n呢啲又唔係賣毒"},{"pid":"aa8dcc7b6d304db1bcf6ace756b8275fd5f0894e","tid":2200281,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63fdb2a44c8cdea703426b114152666d84be6848","tid":2200281,"uid":228169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:46:56.000Z","msg":"消委會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:49:13.000Z","msg":"試過？<img src=\"/ass